Amber heard, Ex-wife of Johnny Depp accused him for physically abusing her, and has also accused him of throwing a phone at her face, which she says left her bruised!

We want Johnny Depp back in the the movie he was the main reason we loved that movie so if he's not in it! We won't watch the movie.
